# grunt-electron-compile

> Precompile electron app source files with [electron-compile](http://github.com/electronjs/electron-compile)

[![dependencies](https://img.shields.io/david/jgeurts/grunt-electron-compile.svg)](https://david-dm.org/jgeurts/grunt-electron-compile)

## Install

```
$ npm install --save-dev grunt-electron-compile
```


## Usage

```js
require('load-grunt-tasks')(grunt); // npm install --save-dev load-grunt-tasks

grunt.initConfig({
	"electron-compile": {
	  dist: {
      files: [{
        expand: true,
        cwd: '.',
        src: ['src/**/*.*', 'static/index.html', 'static/js/**/*.*']
      }],
      options: {
        targetDir: './cache'
      }
	  }
	}
});

grunt.registerTask('default', ['electron-compile']);
```


